===幸福商場===
幸福商場樓高2層，設多間日用品商店，包括[[百佳超級市場|百佳超級市場]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=店舖一覽|url=https://www.parknshop.com/zh-hk/storeLocator|author=百佳網上超級市場|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2018-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180707190122/http://www.parknshop.com/zh-hk/storeLocator|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[7-11便利店|7-11便利店]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=7-Eleven 喺邊?|url=https://www.7-eleven.com.hk/zh/store|accessdate=|author=7-Eleven® Hong Kong|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410010944/https://www.7-eleven.com.hk/zh/store|dead-url=no}}</ref>、香港專業滾軸溜冰鞋專門店<ref>{{Cite web|title=聯絡我們|url=http://www.pro-skate.com.hk/shop/contact/|author=PRO SKATE香港專業滾軸溜冰鞋專門店|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226064953/http://www.pro-skate.com.hk/shop/contact/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、屋苑智能迷你倉<ref>{{Cite web|title=EasyBox收納易迷你倉|url=http://www.easybox.com.hk|author=EasyBox收納易迷你倉|access-date=2022-06-25|archive-date=2022-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220419034459/https://easybox.com.hk/}}</ref>、參茸海味行、文具店、中醫診所和眼鏡店等。餐廳包括賓墟茶餐廳、包點先生、君日餐廳、[[大家樂|大家樂]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Café de Coral - 分店資料|url=https://www.cafedecoralfastfood.com/shops.php?lang=b5&district=34|author=大家樂|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403000545/http://cafedecoralfastfood.com/shops.php?lang=b5&district=34|dead-url=no}}</ref>、Chubby's Pizza和小食店“和你食”等。

